  "rawText": "GRAMMAR 初中英语 语法 精练\n第1章 名词\nI. 选择填空。\n( B ) 1) I need ______ scissors to cut the paper.\nA. any  B. many  C. much  D. lot of\n( A ) 2) Don't eat ______ chocolate. It's bad for your teeth.\nA. a  B. a pair of  C. a piece of  D. two\n( B ) 3) We need huge amounts of ______ about computers.\nA. too much  B. so much  C. too many  D. so many\n( B ) 4) We have ______ in our new flat.\nA. books  B. notes  C. newspapers  D. information\n( D ) 5) You may find ______ rubbish at a building site.\nA. much furniture  B. many furnitures  C. plenty furniture  D. a lot of furnitures\n( B ) 6) Mr. and Mrs. Green are a happy ______.\nA. many  B. a lot of  C. plenty  D. amount of\n( A ) 7) Electrical appliances are powered by ______.\nA. pair  B. group  C. couple  D. people\n( A ) 8) Would the students like to have a discussion on ______ in class?\nA. electric  B. electricity  C. electricities  D. electrics\n( A ) 9) What ______ we are having today!\nA. a pollution  B. pollution  C. some pollutions  D. some pollutions\n( B ) 10) Li Dong is a friend of my ______. We often play card games together.\nA. brother  B. brothers  C. brother's  D. brother's\n( C ) 2) The children enjoyed themselves at the ______ Palace.\nA. Childrens'  B. Children  C. Children's  D. Childrens'\n( B ) 3) It's twenty ______ walk from my home to school.\nA. minute  B. minutes  C. minute's  D. minutes'\n( D ) 4) Is there any news in ______ newspaper?\nA. today  B. today's  C. todays'  D. today of\n( D ) 5) ______ explosive was used for making roads.\nA. such a nice weather  B. a nice weather  C. so nice a weather  D. nice weather\nII. 名词所有格\n选择填空。",
